@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sdbckc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v2 / v1)
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.74 - v0 + 0.37)) + wp.exp(v2))
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.87) + wp.cos((tmp + 0.61 / tmp + 0.44)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(v1 + 0.94)) / tmp)
    v0 = (wp.cos((v2 + 1.00 * v0 + 0.13)) * ((v2 + 0.41 + tmp + 0.67) - (tmp + 0.33 - v1 + 0.95)))
    data[tid] = v0
